{"name": "overlay-arrows-and-more", "metadata": {"name": "overlay-arrows-and-more", "version": "0.5.0", "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 5 - Production/Stable", "Environment :: Console", "Environment :: Win32 (MS Windows)", "Intended Audience :: Developers", "Intended Audience :: End Users/Desktop", "Intended Audience :: System Administrators", "License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Operating System :: Microsoft :: Windows", "Programming Language :: Python :: 2.7", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.8", "Topic :: Software Development :: Testing", "Topic :: Software Development :: User Interfaces"], "home_page": "https://github.com/beuaaa/overlay_arrows_and_more", "license": "MIT", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["pywin32"], "summary": "overlay arrows and more", "upload_time": 1621501419}, "documentation": ["---\nsubstitutions:\n  License: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-yellow.svg\n    :alt: Repository License\n    :target: https://opensource.org/licenses/MIT/\n    ```\n  PyPI version: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/overlay-arrows-and-more.svg\n    :target: https://pypi.org/project/overlay-arrows-and-more/\n    ```\n---\n\n{{ PyPI version }} {{ License }}\n\n# Overlay arrays and more\n\n**WARNING:**\nThis library is still at a very early stage of development.\n\n## Description\n\nThe 'Overlay arrays and more' library displays a transparent window on top of all other windows. The transparent window serves as a support for adding graphical elements such as arrows, rectangles, circles, text, etc...\n\n## Installation\n\n> pip install overlay_arrows_and_more\n\n## Usage\n\nThis is a simple example:\n\n```c\nimport overlay_arrays_and_more as oaam\nimport time\n\nmain_overlay = oaam.Overlay()\ntransparent_overlay = oaam.Overlay(transparency=128)\n\ntransparent_overlay.add(geometry=oaam.Shape.rectangle, x=300, y=300, width=100, height=100, thickness=10, color=(0, 255, 0))\ntransparent_overlay.refresh()\n\nmain_overlay.add(geometry=oaam.Shape.ellipse, x=10, y=10, width=40, height=40)\nmain_overlay.add(geometry=oaam.Shape.rectangle, x=100, y=100, width=100, height=100, color=(0, 0, 255))\nmain_overlay.add(geometry=oaam.Shape.rectangle, x=300, y=100, width=100, height=100, thickness=10, color=(0, 255, 0))\nmain_overlay.refresh()\n\ntime.sleep(9.0)\nmain_overlay.clear_all()\nmain_overlay.refresh()\n```\n\n### Functions\n\nTo be completed\n"], "modules": [{"name": "overlay_arrows_and_more", "documentation": ["To be documented", "-*- coding: utf-8 -*-"], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "overlay_arrows_and_more.__version__", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "overlay_arrows_and_more.overlay", "documentation": ["-*- coding: utf-8 -*-"], "functions": [{"name": "overlay_arrows_and_more.overlay.load_png", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "filename", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "size_x", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "size_y", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "overlay_arrows_and_more.overlay.load_ico", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "filename", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "size_x", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "size_y", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "variables": [{"name": "overlay_arrows_and_more.overlay.CreateIconFromResourceEx", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "overlay_arrows_and_more.overlay.main_overlay", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "overlay_arrows_and_more.overlay.transparent_overlay", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "overlay_arrows_and_more.overlay.hicon", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "overlay_arrows_and_more.overlay.animated_overlay", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "overlay_arrows_and_more.overlay.a", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [{"name": "overlay_arrows_and_more.overla